usdHdlcAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the HDLC component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdHdlcAgentV1.name: usdHdlcAgentV1
usdHdlcAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the HDLC component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the HDLC component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 1.0 system release.
usdHdlcAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the HDLC application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when rsHdlcIfDataPolarity was added.

usdHdlcAgentV2.name: usdHdlcAgentV2
usdHdlcAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the HDLC component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the HDLC component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 1.1 thru 3.0 system releases.
usdHdlcAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the HDLC application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when more objects were added.

usdHdlcAgentV3.name: usdHdlcAgentV3
usdHdlcAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the HDLC component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the HDLC component is supported in the Unisphere
        RX 3.1 and subsequent system releases.
usdHdlcAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the HDLC application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
